data.description: WELCOME HOME!  Home is ready for Move In, you do not want to miss this one!  Three Bedrooms with two full baths, both baths are updated.  Master Bedroom offers full bath, & his/her closets.  Kitchen with plenty of cabinets, double sinks, electric stove, pantry, refrigerator to stay.  Carpeting thru-out, Living Room & Dining Room, Family room with sliding door leading to leveled fenced backyard.  Garage offers additional exit/entry from rear, nice size patio for family barbeques. Full size basement.  New HVAC system July (2023), Water Heater (1 Year).  A must see, make your appointment today!
